They are like variables that control your robot’s behavior without changing the code.

If you have a robot node:

speed = 5 → how fast robot moves
camera_on = true → camera enabled or not

These are ROS 2 parameters.


ros2 commands to assign a value (parameters)
"ros2 run 'package_name' 'topic_name' --ros-args -p data1:='' -p data2:='' "
